profile.bio: Open Source advocate, core member of CakePHP, organizer of CakeFest (annual CakePHP conference), director of the Cake Development Corporation (CakeDC), author of the CakePHP 2 Application CookBook (Packt Publishing), author of the XHTTP and DocML specs.
